long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
AI Garage is a browser extension that provides quick access to a collection of NLP & AI powered tools and utilities. Upgrade & optimise your browsing experience!

The extension includes tools for research paper exploration, resume and cover letter auto-reviewing, task planning, meme generation, smart contract code generation, chat history analysis, travel planner assistant, and more... 

With the v1.5 of the AI Garage extension, users can improve their productivity and access a variety of new AI solutions directly on top of their browser.
